        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> change 'listchars' `trail` default to `⣿`.\n\nI agree with this change, but that character does not appear on really basic terminals (like the Linux terminal). Either the character should be changed or Nvim should fallback to a different symbol when it detects a terminal lacking support for that character.",
            "created_at": "2026-05-05T22:08:07Z",
